-- Application uses Spring Boot --
The MVC Server listens on port 8080
http://localhost:8080/

The application works as follows:
1. Upon receiving above url, it responds with a form that contains 3 numbers asking client to sum them
2. Client enters and sum and submits the form
3. If sum is correct the application responds with 'Success' else an error message and the next challenge


Test Classes are located in test

The project is developed using IntelliJ




